OL,3,C'I've got a kid': Mum's pleas to
OL,4,Cdriver moments before fatal crash
OL,6,FA driver who ignored a teenage mum's
OL,7,Fpleas to stop during a police chase
OL,8,Fhas been jailed for causing her death
OL,9,Fby dangerous driving.
OL,11,FJordan Spalding was behind the wheel
OL,12,Fof a #600 Vauxhall Vectra, which had
OL,13,Fbeen bought earlier that day by
OL,14,FShakeel Ahmed, when he lost control
OL,15,Fand crashed in Baildon, near Bradford,
OL,16,Fin January 2023.
OL,18,FThe car, which had been travelling at
OL,19,Fover 60mph, hit a garden wall and
OL,20,Fflipped over.
