OL,3,C'I've got a kid': Mum's pleas to
OL,4,Cdriver moments before fatal crash
OL,6,FAmber Deakin, an 18-year-old who was
OL,7,Fone of four passengers sitting in the
OL,8,Fback, suffered a fatal head injury.
OL,10,FBradford Crown Court heard she had
OL,11,Fshouted at Spalding during the
OL,12,Fpursuit: "I've got a kid. Just stop
OL,13,Fplease. I need to get home to my kid."
OL,15,FSpalding, who only held a provisional
OL,16,Flicence and was not insured, had to be
OL,17,Fhelped to drive the car by Ahmed, who
OL,18,Fhad been operating the loose gear-
OL,19,Fstick from the front passenger seat
OL,20,Fduring the pursuit.
