OL,6,FSpalding was trapped in the car and
OL,7,Fhad to be cut free, but the court
OL,8,Fheard that Ahmed fled the scene.
OL,10,FSpalding, 23, of Wharncliffe Crescent,
OL,11,FBradford, pleaded guilty to causing
OL,12,Fdeath by dangerous driving and was
OL,13,Fjailed for nine years and 10 months.
OL,15,FAhmed, 29, of Moresby Road, Bradford,
OL,16,Fpleaded guilty to aiding and abetting
OL,17,FSpalding's dangerous driving. He was
OL,18,Fjailed for 11 years and one month.
