OL,3,C'I've got a kid': Mum's pleas to
OL,4,Cdriver moments before fatal crash
OL,6,FBoth men will have to serve 10-year
OL,7,Fdriving bans after they are released
OL,8,Ffrom prison.
OL,10,FThe Recorder of Bradford Judge
OL,11,FJonathan Rose said Amber, the mother
OL,12,Fof a then 18-month-old child, had her
OL,13,Flife "stolen" by the defendants'
OL,14,F"irresponsible, dangerous and utterly
OL,15,Fabhorrent" driving.
