OL,6,FJudge Rose said Spalding ignored
OL,7,FAmber's pleas to stop.
OL,9,F"Instead you transformed this from an
OL,10,Fidiotic and potentially dangerous
OL,11,Fpiece of driving into driving that
OL,12,Fwhich would almost inevitably end in
OL,13,Fan accident, a crash, injury and
OL,14,Fdeath," the judge told Spalding.
OL,16,FAmber's mother Hayley Norton said in a
OL,17,Fstatement that since the incident her
OL,18,Flife had been filled with "unbearable
OL,19,Fsorrow".
