OL,6,F"I find myself unable to focus on
OL,7,Fanything, consumed by the pain of
OL,8,Flosing my daughter," she said.
OL,10,F"The emptiness I feel is overwhelming
OL,11,Fand the world no longer seems as
OL,12,Fbright without her in it."
OL,14,FDet Con Lindsey Pickles, of the West
OL,15,FYorkshire Police Major Collision
OL,16,FEnquiry Team, said: "This is the stark
OL,17,Freality of the consequences of driving
OL,18,Fdangerously on the roads, her death
OL,19,Fcould have been avoided.
